A lot of twists and deaths. I feel like: The worst Star Wars entry excluding the prequels.  Weirdly paced\, underwhelming visuals\, too many characters to focus on\, boring subplots\, poorly executed comedy\, and a ridiculous amount of deus ex machina.  The only thing this movie did well was it's execution of Kylo Ren's story.  [2/10]
